<div class="modal" id="m-geo" data-t="c"><div class="modal-bg" onclick="CM('m-geo')"></div><div class="modal-box"><div class="m-accent"></div><div class="m-hdr"><button class="m-close" onclick="CM('m-geo')">✕</button><span class="m-tag">Computer Vision · AI · Python · Mar 2026</span><h2 class="m-title">GeoVision AI — Lawgorith</h2><p class="m-sub">AI-powered drone imagery analysis for infrastructure detection & geospatial intelligence</p></div><div class="m-prog" id="mp-geo"></div><div class="m-body"><div class="ms"><h4>Overview</h4><p>Replaces slow traditional land survey methods. Auto-detects buildings, roads, water bodies & utility assets from drone imagery, exporting GeoJSON for professional GIS platforms.</p></div><div class="ms"><h4>Architecture</h4><div class="arch"><div class="ab">Drone Image</div><div class="aa">→</div><div class="ab">CV Preprocessing</div><div class="aa">→</div><div class="ab">Feature Detection</div><div class="aa">→</div><div class="ab">Geo Conversion</div><div class="aa">→</div><div class="ab">GeoJSON Export</div></div></div><div class="ms"><h4>Features</h4><ul><li>Building detection & classification</li><li>Road network extraction and spatial mapping</li><li>Water body identification</li><li>GeoJSON export for any GIS platform</li><li>Streamlit UI: drag-and-drop + live results</li></ul></div><div class="ms"><h4>Stack</h4><div class="mc"><span>Python 3.10</span><span>OpenCV</span><span>NumPy</span><span>Streamlit</span><span>GeoJSON</span></div></div><div class="ms"><h4>Repository</h4><div class="ml"><a class="mp" href="https://github.com/yashvendranirwan-alt/Geo-vision-Ai-" target="_blank">⬡ GitHub →</a></div></div></div></div></div>

<div class="modal" id="m-vax" data-t="v"><div class="modal-bg" onclick="CM('m-vax')"></div><div class="modal-box"><div class="m-accent"></div><div class="m-hdr"><button class="m-close" onclick="CM('m-vax')">✕</button><span class="m-tag">IoT · AI · Blockchain · C++ · Jan–Mar 2026</span><h2 class="m-title">VaxSafe — Cold Chain Monitor</h2><p class="m-sub">ESP32 edge sensing + AI potency model + SHA-256 custody chain. Warehouse to patient.</p></div><div class="m-prog" id="mp-vax"></div><div class="m-body"><div class="ms"><div style="margin-bottom:14px"><span style="font-family:var(--fm);font-size:9px;padding:3px 9px;background:rgba(245,158,11,.07);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.2);color:var(--a);letter-spacing:.1em">🏆 4th Place — Projectathon 2026</span></div><h4>Overview</h4><p>ESP32+DHT22 monitors vaccine temperature in real-time. Flask AI computes potency decay. Every update SHA-256 hashed — immutable chain of custody.</p></div><div class="ms"><h4>Architecture</h4><div class="arch"><div class="ab">ESP32+DHT22</div><div class="aa">→</div><div class="ab">Edge Alert</div><div class="aa">→</div><div class="ab">Flask Server</div><div class="aa">→</div><div class="ab">AI Potency</div><div class="aa">→</div><div class="ab">SHA-256 Chain</div></div></div><div class="ms"><h4>Hardware</h4><ul><li>ESP32 WiFi+BLE microcontroller</li><li>DHT22 (GPIO 15) — temp & humidity</li><li>Red LED (GPIO 12) — breach alert</li><li>Buzzer (GPIO 13) — audible alarm</li><li>Blynk IoT Cloud — remote dashboard</li></ul></div><div class="ms"><h4>AI Decay Model</h4><ul><li>Heat: 1°C above 8°C → potency −0.1%</li><li>Freeze: below 2°C → potency −0.5%</li><li>Hash: SHA256(temp+health+timestamp+prev)</li></ul></div><div class="ms"><h4>Stack</h4><div class="mc"><span>C++</span><span>Python</span><span>Flask</span><span>ESP32</span><span>SHA-256</span><span>Blynk IoT</span></div></div><div class="ms"><h4>Repos</h4><div class="ml"><a class="mp" href="https://github.com/yashvendranirwan-alt/vaxsafe-" target="_blank">⬡ Core System →</a><a href="https://github.com/yashvendranirwan-alt/vaxsafesite" target="_blank">⬡ Web Interface →</a></div></div></div></div></div>

<div class="modal" id="m-shop" data-t="a"><div class="modal-bg" onclick="CM('m-shop')"></div><div class="modal-box"><div class="m-accent"></div><div class="m-hdr"><button class="m-close" onclick="CM('m-shop')">✕</button><span class="m-tag">E-Commerce · Shopify · UI/UX · Mar 2026</span><h2 class="m-title">Vibe Gadgets — E-Commerce Store</h2><p class="m-sub">Fully launched Shopify store — zero to live, entirely solo</p></div><div class="m-prog" id="mp-shop"></div><div class="m-body"><div class="ms"><h4>Overview</h4><p>Designed and launched a complete Shopify gadget store. Mobile-first responsive design, optimised purchase flow, full store operations from listings to payment gateways and shipping.</p></div><div class="ms"><h4>What Was Built</h4><ul><li>Fully responsive storefront — mobile-first design</li><li>Product listings with optimised descriptions & pricing</li><li>Secure payment gateway integration</li><li>Shipping rules and fulfillment configuration</li><li>Navigation optimised for product discovery</li><li>SEO — meta titles, alt text, URL structure</li></ul></div><div class="ms"><h4>Stack</h4><div class="mc"><span>Shopify</span><span>Liquid</span><span>UI/UX</span><span>Payment Integration</span><span>SEO</span><span>Canva</span></div></div></div></div></div>

